The road to Anina is passable and in good condition. Route 58 is one of the most beautiful and well maintained roads.
Anina town is located at:
• about 32 km from the city of Resita, on Route 58;
• 33 Km from the city Oravita, on Route 57B;
• 34 Km from the city Bozovici, on Route 57B.

Anina town is located in the central part of the county and is bordered by
as follows:

• Southwest - the village Romanian Ciclova;

• South - Great Lapusnicu commune;

• East - Bozovici commune;

• North - West - Ciudanovita commune;

• North - Carasova commune;

• West - with Oravita city.


For more information, ask any person you meet and you’ll find that they know everything about the area!
